skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my love card
des: Ask Alexa for your daily Love Card, and she'll read Angel's top pick for you. (Each answer is based on a Tarot Card.) You can ask as often as you like, and for as many friends and relatives as you wish. Enjoy!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
